---
title: "transferForSwap - FeeAggregator Asset Transfer (Payment Abstraction V2)"
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB
    [*] --> q_check_role: transferForSwap(asset, amount, to) called
    q_check_role --> q_check_allowlist: caller has SWAPPER_ROLE
    q_check_role --> q_revert_role: unauthorized
    q_revert_role --> [*]: revert Unauthorized
    q_check_allowlist --> q_check_amount: asset in allowlisted assets
    q_check_allowlist --> q_revert_allowlist: asset not allowlisted
    q_revert_allowlist --> [*]: revert AssetNotAllowlisted
    q_check_amount --> q_check_balance: amount > 0
    q_check_amount --> q_revert_amount: amount == 0
    q_revert_amount --> [*]: revert InvalidAmount
    q_check_balance --> q_transfer: balance >= amount
    q_check_balance --> q_revert_balance: insufficient balance
    q_revert_balance --> [*]: revert InsufficientBalance
    q_transfer --> [*]: transfer asset tokens to recipient

    note right of q_check_allowlist
        INV-001: SWAPPER_ROLE granted only to GPV2CompatibleAuction contract
        INV-002: Only allowlisted assets can be transferred
        INV-003: Allowlists must be synchronized between FeeAggregator and auction contract
    end note
